message:
In src/types/mastery.ts, add the following interface:

export interface BoundaryNote {
  id: string;
  note: string;
  timestamp: string;
}

Then, update the VocabWord interface in the same file to include a boundaryNotes field:

export interface VocabWord {
  id: string;
  word: string;
  partOfSpeech: string;
  meanings: string;
  confidenceScore: number;
  status: MasteryStatus;
  useCount: number;
  frequencyRank: number;
  isMasteryCandidate: boolean;
  sessionNotes: string;
  boundaryNotes: BoundaryNote[];
}

Once those changes are made, stage all changes, commit with the message "fix: add missing BoundaryNote type and update VocabWord interface", and push to GitHub.
